                 oldref="32"><switchinline select="appl"><caseinline select="DRAW">Grid to Front
</caseinline><caseinline select="IMPRESS">Grid to Front
</caseinline></switchinline></paragraph>
      <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" id="par_id3153573" role="paragraph" l10n="CHG" oldref="33"><switchinline select="appl"><caseinline select="DRAW">Sets the visible grid in front of all objects.
